Paris is concerned about the links between Al Qaeda in the Islamic Maghreb and the Boko Haram sect.
The links between Al Qaeda terrorist group in the Islamic Maghreb (Aqmi) and the Nigerian sect of Boko Haram, which had long been suspected, have been confirmed.
On Sunday, Algerian Deputy Minister for Foreign Affairs Abdelkader Messahel even stated that Algiers already "has certainty".
